OL,3,CMan banned from football matches after
OL,4,Cgetting caught with cocaine
OL,6,FA football banning order has been
OL,7,Fgiven to a man who was caught with
OL,8,Fdrugs before a Gillingham FC match.
OL,10,FIt happened while Kent Police officers
OL,11,Fwere running an operation outside
OL,12,FPriestfield Stadium with drug
OL,13,Fdetection dogs in December 2023.
OL,15,FShortly before kick-off in the FA Cup
OL,16,Ffixture against Charlton Athletic, the
OL,17,Fman, 31, from Chatham came to the
OL,18,Fattention of police dog, Dougal.
