OL,3,CMan banned from football matches after
OL,4,Cgetting caught with cocaine
OL,6,FHe had travelled to the game with his
OL,7,Fchild and friend and was detained for
OL,8,Fa search. He dropped a small packet of
OL,9,Fwhite powder onto the floor, which was
OL,10,Flater confirmed to be cocaine.
OL,12,FThe man was arrested and charged with
OL,13,Fbeing in possession of a class A drug.
OL,15,FHe told officers that he'd forgotten
OL,16,Fit had been in his pocket for several
OL,17,Fweeks and that he was not intending to
OL,18,Ftake into the ground.
