OL,3,CMan banned from football matches after
OL,4,Cgetting caught with cocaine
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty at Medway
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on January 17 and
OL,8,Freceived an 18-month conditional
OL,9,Fdischarge, in addition to the Football
OL,10,FBanning Order.
OL,12,FIt means he's prevented from attending
OL,13,Fany regulated matches for the next
OL,14,Fthree years.
OL,16,FPolice say those planning on taking
OL,17,Fdrugs to football matches should be
OL,18,Fwarned that it could be the last one
OL,19,Fthey attend for a number of years.
