OL,3,CMan banned from football matches after
OL,4,Cgetting caught with cocaine
OL,6,FChief Inspector Alan Rogers of Kent
OL,7,FPolice's Tactical Operations Command
OL,8,Fsaid: "Gillingham FC and other
OL,9,Ffootball clubs across Kent are
OL,10,Fcommitted to making the matchday
OL,11,Fexperience as family-friendly as
OL,12,Fpossible.
OL,14,F"One of the ways they do so is by
OL,15,Fmaking their stadium a no-go area for
OL,16,Fdrug users.
