OL,3,CMan banned from football matches after
OL,4,Cgetting caught with cocaine
OL,6,F"We are fully supportive of their
OL,7,Fefforts to help tackle the possession
OL,8,Fof illegal substances and we look
OL,9,Fforward to holding similar operations
OL,10,Fat Priestfield in the future.
OL,12,F"Anyone planning on taking drugs to a
OL,13,Ffootball match should take this
OL,14,Foutcome as a warning that it could be
OL,15,Fthe last they attend for a number of
OL,16,Fyears."
